# VHS tape for the quantedge-ta-example demo GIF.
# Install: https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs
# Render:  vhs demo.tape  (produces demo.gif)

Output demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

Type "cargo run"
Enter
Sleep 14s
Ctrl+C
Sleep 4s
